156\\\" extraction_method: \\\"native-text\\\" extracted_at: \\\"2026-07-21T06:50:10.4577228Z\\\" terminology_sources: - standard: \\\"CDISC\\\" model: \\\"CDASHIG\\\" publication: \\\"Clinical Data Acquisition Standards Harmonization Implementation Guide for Human Clinical Trials\\\" version: \\\"2.1\\\" publication_date: \\\"2019-11-01\\\" source_url: \\\"https://www.cdisc.org/standards/foundational/cdashig-v2-1\\\" retrieved_at: \\\"2026-07-21T07:02:36.5931875Z\\\" - standard: \\\"CDISC\\\" model: \\\"Controlled Terminology\\\" publication: \\\"CDISC Controlled Terminology - CDASH and SDTM\\\" version: \\\"2026-03-27\\\" source_url: \\\"https://www.cdisc.org/standards/terminology/controlled-terminology\\\" retrieved_at: \\\"2026-07-21T07:02:36.5931875Z\\\" - standard: \\\"CDISC\\\" model: \\\"QRS Supplement\\\" publication: \\\"Mini-Mental State Examination\\\" version: \\\"1.0\\\" publication_date: \\\"2024-12-12\\\" source_url: \\\"https://www.cdisc.org/standards/foundational/qrs/mini-mental-state-examination\\\" retrieved_at: \\\"2026-07-21T07:02:36.5931875Z\\\" access_note: \\\"The official page confirms the FT domain, MMSE category, version, and release date; detailed supplement files require authenticated CDISC access.\\\" - standard: \\\"CDISC/NCI EVS\\\" model: \\\"SDTM Controlled Terminology\\\" publication: \\\"SDTM Terminology\\\" version: \\\"2026-03-27\\\" source_url: \\\"https://evs.nci.nih.gov/ftp1/CDISC/SDTM/SDTM%20Terminology.txt\\\" retrieved_at: \\\"2026-07-21T07:02:36.5931875Z\\\" sha256: \\\"bf463677654171d701d09ffcb0a122e9523029b42d542269f45fb496a35ecef9\\\" study_summary: design: \\\"Multicentre, evaluator-blinded, randomised, parallel-controlled trial\\\" planned_enrolment: 148 population: \\\"Han adults aged 30-65 years with newly diagnosed moderate-to-severe obstructive sleep apnoea\\\" arms: - \\\"CPAP plus best supportive care\\\" - \\\"Best supportive care only\\\" randomisation_ratio: \\\"1:1\\\" scheduled_assessments: - \\\"baseline