ined.\\\" affected_concepts: - \\\"inc02_age_30_to_65\\\" - \\\"inc03_osa_diagnostic_criterion\\\" - \\\"inc04_cpap_tolerance\\\" - \\\"exc07_mmse_below_24\\\" source_refs: - locator: \\\"Eligibility criteria, pages 2-3\\\" resolution: \\\"The user approved the full criterion worksheet plus separate evidence values for age, AHI, one-night CPAP use, and MMSE.\\\" resolved_by: \\\"user decision in Codex task\\\" resolved_at: \\\"2026-07-21\\\" - id: \\\"U-012\\\" severity: \\\"blocking\\\" question: \\\"Approve criterion-level capture for compound exclusions 5 and 13, or request separate evidence fields for each substance, medication, disease, and treatment.\\\" affected_concepts: - \\\"exc05_substance_or_restricted_medication\\\" - \\\"exc13_recent_treatment_listed_condition\\\" source_refs: - locator: \\\"Exclusion criteria items 5 and 13, pages 2-3\\\" resolution: \\\"The user approved retaining exclusions 5 and 13 as single compound protocol-level criteria.\\\" resolved_by: \\\"user decision in Codex task\\\" resolved_at: \\\"2026-07-21\\\" - id: \\\"U-013\\\" severity: \\\"blocking\\\" question: \\\"Confirm whether the final eligible-for-randomisation field should remain a manual investigator confirmation rather than an automatically calculated value.\\\" affected_concepts: - \\\"eligible_for_randomisation\\\" source_refs: - locator: \\\"Flow diagram, page 3; Randomisation, page 4\\\" resolution: \\\"The user approved a manual investigator eligibility determination with consistency checks; the form must not silently overwrite the decision.\\\" resolved_by: \\\"user decision in Codex task\\\" resolved_at: \\\"2026-07-21\\\" - id: \\\"U-014\\\" severity: \\\"blocking\\\" question: \\\"Provide or approve the sponsor study identifier and the five site identifiers; the trial registration number and institution names must not be silently substituted.\\\" affected_concepts: - \\\"study_identifier\\\" - \\\"site_identifier\\\" source_refs: - locator: \\\"Protocol title a