\" - \\\"source.protocol_date\\\" source_refs: - locator: \\\"Article header, page 1\\\" resolution: null resolved_by: null resolved_at: null - id: \\\"U-003\\\" severity: \\\"blocking\\\" question: \\\"For the selected form, which fields are mandatory? The protocol generally does not state field-level requiredness.\\\" affected_concepts: - \\\"selected_form.fields.required\\\" source_refs: - locator: \\\"Outcome assessment and study examination procedures, pages 4-6\\\" resolution: \\\"The user approved the Gate A proposal: all core screening fields are required; investigator_unsuitable_reason is conditionally required when exc16 is Y; calculated BMI is read-only and is not independently required.\\\" resolved_by: \\\"user decision in Codex task\\\" resolved_at: \\\"2026-07-21\\\" - id: \\\"U-004\\\" severity: \\\"blocking\\\" question: \\\"For the selected form, confirm the data types, units, precision, and edit-check ranges that the protocol does not explicitly define.\\\" affected_concepts: - \\\"selected_form.fields.data_type\\\" - \\\"selected_form.fields.unit\\\" - \\\"selected_form.fields.range\\\" source_refs: - locator: \\\"Outcome and procedure descriptions, pages 4-6\\\" resolution: \\\"The user approved the proposed data types, protocol units and threshold consistency checks. Unstated plausible-data ranges and precision remain unset; BMI displays two decimal places per the user's implementation request.\\\" resolved_by: \\\"user decision in Codex task\\\" resolved_at: \\\"2026-07-21\\\" - id: \\\"U-005\\\" severity: \\\"warning\\\" question: \\\"At which visits are lung function and ECG performed? They are exceptions to the general baseline/3/6/12-month schedule, but the alternative schedule is not stated.\\\" affected_concepts: - \\\"lung_function.visit_schedule\\\" - \\\"ecg.visit_schedule\\\" source_refs: - locator: \\\"Study examination procedures, page 5\\\" resolution: null resolved_by: null resolved_at: null - id: \\\"U-006\\\" severity: \\\"bloc