able status for the supporting OSA diagnosis, AHI, one-night CPAP-use duration, and investigator-rationale fields.\\\" affected_concepts: - \\\"newly_diagnosed_osa\\\" - \\\"screening_ahi\\\" - \\\"cpap_one_night_use_hours\\\" - \\\"investigator_unsuitable_reason\\\" source_refs: - locator: \\\"Inclusion criteria items 3-4, page 2; Exclusion criteria item 16, page 3\\\" resolution: \\\"The user approved the Gate A recommendations: PR.PROCCUR for PSG completion; not-applicable to CDASHIG v2.1 for newly-diagnosed OSA, screening AHI, one-night CPAP-use hours, and investigator rationale, each with the documented rationale.\\\" resolved_by: \\\"user decision in Codex task\\\" resolved_at: \\\"2026-07-21\\\" - id: \\\"U-017\\\" severity: \\\"blocking\\\" question: \\\"Approve or reject the official MMSE total-score candidate FT.FTORRES with FTCAT=MMSE, FTTESTCD=MMS112, FTTEST=MMS1-Total Score, and NCIt C100586.\\\" affected_concepts: - \\\"mmse_score\\\" source_refs: - locator: \\\"Exclusion criteria item 7, page 3\\\" resolution: \\\"The user approved FT.FTORRES with FTCAT=MMSE, FTTESTCD=MMS112, FTTEST=MMS1-Total Score, and NCIt C100586 for total-score capture.\\\" resolved_by: \\\"user decision in Codex task\\\" resolved_at: \\\"2026-07-21\\\" - id: \\\"U-018\\\" severity: \\\"blocking\\\" question: \\\"Approve replacing software Boolean fields with CDISC-coded string radio fields using Y (Yes, NCIt C49488) and N (No, NCIt C49487) from codelist C66742 for all Yes/No eligibility responses.\\\" affected_concepts: - \\\"inc01_informed_consent\\\" - \\\"inc02_age_30_to_65\\\" - \\\"newly_diagnosed_osa\\\" - \\\"full_night_lab_psg_completed\\\" - \\\"inc03_osa_diagnostic_criterion\\\" - \\\"inc04_cpap_tolerance\\\" - \\\"inc05_no_other_trial_last_3_months\\\" - \\\"inc06_able_complete_tests_followup\\\" - \\\"exc01_severe_systemic_disease\\\" - \\\"exc02_psychiatric_condition\\\" - \\\"exc03_neurological_disease\\\" - \\\"exc04_other_sleep_disorder\\\" - \\\"exc05_substance_